INSERT INTO `teams` VALUES (4,'MR. CHAN DARA','MR. ចាន់ ដារ៉ា','General Manager','អ្នកគ្រប់គ្រងទូទៅ','/teams/CamGoTech_3yVHfIEc6R8qDJwU54ONg4wK9Q4YVRdHpiCAIGrT.jpg','https://www.facebook.com/','','','',2,1,'2024-08-31 21:34:56','2024-09-17 11:18:06','General Manager',''),(5,'MS. RACHANA CHEA','','Events Management','','/teams/CamGoTech_ps8OOFILJ2r8lkVHienOl6RdwhiYGNM28KOj9p3g.jpg','','','','',3,1,'2024-09-02 20:41:06','2024-09-17 11:20:10','Events Management',''),(6,'MS. DAVIKA SO','','HR Management','','/teams/CamGoTech_PKzi061AzkrIUYeAcvyxq8vOajgh2YGC0EvImDXk.jpg','','','','',4,1,'2024-09-02 20:43:24','2024-09-17 11:20:30','HR Management',''),(7,'Chee Boreth','','Professional Background\n2002 - Present\nMr. Chee Boreth serves as the Executive Director at the Children Development Association (CDA), where he leads efforts to empower underprivileged communities through educational and health initiatives that support holistic child development. His leadership at CDA has been marked by innovative approaches to community intervention and program implementation that have significantly improved the lives of many children and their families.\nDonation-Based Crowdfunding and Project Management\nMr. Boreth has been instrumental in integrating donation-based crowdfunding as a core strategy for financing CDA\'s initiatives. His guidance in this area ensures that fundraising efforts are both effective and engaging, maximizing community support and participation.\nCrowdfunding leading (Donation-Based)\nAs someone deeply involved in donation-based projects, Mr. Boreth offers the following advice and lead on utilizing crowdfunding platforms effectively:\n1.	Engage Your Audience: Create compelling storytelling that connects potential donors with the cause. Clear communication about how their contribution will make a difference is essential to motivating them to donate.\n2.	Transparency is Key: Regularly share detailed updates and transparent reports on how funds are being used. Transparency builds trust and encourages further donations. \n3.	Incentivize Contributions: Although donation campaigns primarily focus on altruism, offering unique thank-you gifts or public acknowledgments can enhance engagement and motivation.\nMr. Boreth’s strategic approach to crowdfunding not only drives financial support but also fosters a sense of community and shared purpose among donors, creating a robust support system for CDA’s various educational and health programs.\nProject Management\nUnder Mr. Boreth\'s leadership, CDA has excelled in project management, implementing numerous initiatives that have brought substantial improvements to underprivileged communities. His expertise in project management ensures that every program is meticulously planned, executed, and evaluated to achieve the desired outcomes. \nKey Elements of Project Management\n1.	Needs Assessment: Conducting comprehensive needs assessments to identify critical areas that require intervention.\n2.	Strategic Planning: Developing detailed strategic plans that outline clear objectives, timelines, and resource allocations.\n3.	Implementation: Overseeing the execution of projects with a focus on efficiency and effectiveness.\n4.	Monitoring and Evaluation: Continuously monitoring progress and evaluating outcomes to make necessary adjustments and ensure success.\nThrough his adept management, Mr. Boreth has successfully navigated numerous challenges, ensuring the sustainability and impact of CDA\'s initiatives. His commitment to excellence in project management has been a cornerstone of the organization\'s success, ensuring that resources are used effectively to maximize benefits for the communities served. \nMr. Chee Boreth\nExecutive Director, Children Development Association','','/teams/CamGoTech_2IucLroNA2EmRY7EDzJCI9ao0wN5nqagMZB8I368.jpg','https://www.facebook.com/','','','',1,1,'2024-09-14 02:51:52','2024-09-17 11:17:35','Executive Director, Children Development Association','');
